measurements.description:
Two hundred thirty-five flowers and six buds on four double-branched inflorescences plus what are apparently older
	un-branched inflorescenses with fewer flowers and some buds, on 96 cm high plant (including inflorescences) grown in 20 cm pot; 
	sepals and petals yellow-green almost completely overlaid red-purple, leaving base color exposed as narrow picotee edge and variously as small spots;
	lip white, three-lobed with lighter red-purple markings;
    substance firm; texture matte.
